item.description: [en] Privacy disclaimer: This site doesn't collect your IP or track you. I don't have Netlify Analytics in my site, so no idea who you are. Tripetto probably tracks your IP and basic metadata to avoid users submitting the form again, but I'm not sure. In any case, I don't collect your IP, Reddit username, or any information that could single out you. This Tripetto form makes some personal question such as age group and country, but you're free to not answer them and go straight to the horoscope
